@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kyvxyz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v2 + 0.89)) / v0)
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp((v1 + 0.82 - v2 + 0.63)))
    tmp = (0.30 / ((v2 + 0.68 - v1 + 0.50) - (v1 + 0.24 + v0 + 0.62)))
    tmp = ((0.87 - v2) + wp.sin((v2 + 0.99 + tmp + 0.01)))
    data[tid] = v0
